body:
Only TF targets that start with "android_" will build for Android, so `//tensorflow/contrib/quantization:cc_ops` is not expected to work here.

Did you clone with `--recurse-submodules`? Alternatively try `tensorflow/contrib/makefile/download_dependencies.sh`
